{"tid":1100767,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助] 點樣救返沉迷賭海嘅朋友?","createTime":"2019-04-10T15:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T14:49:25.000Z","uid":199675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a756ac32237e4e921e62bc484dc798cbea6d6c92","tid":1100767,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個好熟嘅friend年紀唔大 成撚日喺度賭波賭馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前排過關一次過嬴咗成皮返嚟 就好似上哂癮咁 愈買愈大 最後咪又係輸返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家窮到食飯錢都畀唔起 要其他friend請住先 仲諗住繼續賭 翻盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以救吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想睇住佢咁樣落去...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">利申: 有陪佢睇賭海迷徒 但佢邊睇邊開住個馬會apps</span>"},{"pid":"9bf4be9fe38c89d37754046f1a0fc4fa4387ac2a","tid":1100767,"uid":154756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"大賭變李嘉誠"},{"pid":"e6c1255b0e62b8388c5a4f43bac20f21e824366c","tid":1100767,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf4be9fe38c89d37754046f1a0fc4fa4387ac2a","tid":1100767,"uid":154756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"大賭變李嘉誠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"一次係嬴好多 但都會好快輸返 唔識收手"},{"pid":"59f837666f708ba67250b91af64182ed9793be0e","tid":1100767,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"認真答你：<br />\n如果已經去到會輸到要搵朋友請食飯，已經近乎無得救。<br />\n呢類人，賭到連飯錢都輸得，證明佢根本無自制能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你應該同班friend 一齊夾好唔幫佢，等佢飯都無得開，睇下佢會唔會醒。如果仲係賭落去，真係直接當少個朋友算啦。<br />\n<br />\n你要希望你個朋友係因為坐定粒六覺得點仆街都好，仲有你班朋友接濟，所以先賭到咁；而唔係上咗癮唔賭唔自在嗰種。"},{"pid":"7dc156c570d1d290bde131ecc45d578dff43a468","tid":1100767,"uid":207706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0